#

Whole Wheat Waffles

25 min
$5
200 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh Fiber

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastEasyHealthy

Description

Fluffy and wholesome waffles made with whole wheat flour, perfect for a nutritious breakfast on-the-go!

Ingredients

  • whole wheat flour: 1 cup
  • baking powder: 2 tsp
  • baking soda: 1/2 tsp
  • salt: 1/4 tsp
  • milk: 1 cup
  • egg: 1
  • honey or maple syrup: 2 tbsp
  • unsalted butter, melted: 2 tbsp
